replies.body:
{{champion:15}} 
I'm not an adc main, but when I'm left with adc I usually play Sivir. The problem with her is that if you have a bad game people just go "bg %%%% adc lost in champ select sivir useless champ" because she's not meta, and I'd also assume this would be similar with Quinn. Sivir also doesn't have a jump and has a relatively short range, she's fairly dependent on positioning and using your Spell Shield effectively. 

{{champion:51}} 
I'd recommend Cait based on what you've said, she's reasonably simple, long range and does have an ability to reposition. She doesn't carry as hard as most of the others but you're almost always guaranteed to be effective just by standing at the back and auto attacking.
